postAuth.description: Creates an auth. Send the auth payload in the request body and receive the created auth in the response.

postGenerate.description: Creates a generate. Send the generate payload in the request body and receive the created generate in the response.

postTasks.description: Creates a task. Send the task payload in the request body and receive the created task in the response.

putTasks.description: Updates a task. Send the fields to update in the request body and receive the updated task.

deleteTasks.description: Deletes a task. Use this endpoint to remove the task and receive a confirmation response.

postUsers.description: Creates an user. Send the user payload in the request body and receive the created user in the response.

getAuth.description: Reads auth for display or reporting. Use this query to fetch auth with optional filters or pagination.

getGenerate.description: Reads generate for display or reporting. Use this query to fetch generate with optional filters or pagination.

pages.description: Reads pages for display or reporting. Use this query to fetch pages with optional filters or pagination.

getTasks.description: Reads tasks for display or reporting. Use this query to fetch tasks with optional filters or pagination.

getUsers.description: Reads users for display or reporting. Use this query to fetch users with optional filters or pagination.
